      "writtenOn": "2019-07-26T17:11:25Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m kinda torn on this because there is no obvious ownership transfer at this level - the fact that the implementation grabs a ref temporarily is incidental (we could use the fontmgr without reffing in a different impl).\n\nOTOH passing a value allows us to make the parameter optional, which seems nice.\n\nOh, I was in the middle of making the change when I realized ShapeToFit calls ShapeImpl repeatedly in a loop - so passing by value would either force copies or yield some awkward workarounds.  I guess I\u0027m leaning toward deferred ownership transfer after all...",
